	(374,84,'bio','Nature, Psychology, Sociology, Permaculture, The visual and tactile human form, Sexuality, Mycology, The intriguing allure of the ocean, Travel, History, Science, Music, Politics. A short list of what drives me as an artist.\r\n\r\nI look forward to many more collaborations on skin, meeting new people, catching up with those already aquainted, personal expressions on canvas, and capturing of my observations on film over the next 21 years and beyond. I am humbly grateful for the support of my loved ones and my many varied clients past, future, and present without which this life long experience would not be possible.'),
